https://w3id.org/okn/o/sd#description: Interventions concerning fertilizer subsidies can be expressed in this model as a percentage of fertilizer prices.
Interventions that force specific target planting windows can be expressed in this model as a start or end planting date
Interventions concerning weed control and weed management practices can be reflected in this model by indicating the fraction of weeds that will remain after the weed treatments applied by farmers
